# Project Plan

Phase 1 (Weeks 1–2)
- Setup environment
- Understand DBpedia structure

Phase 2 (Weeks 3–6)
- Develop data cleaning scripts
- Detect inconsistencies

Phase 3 (Weeks 7–9)
- Optimize SPARQL queries
- Performance testing

Phase 4 (Weeks 10–12)
- Build visualization dashboard
- Final documentation

import pandas as pd

# Load dataset
df = pd.read_csv('data/sample_data.csv')

# Show missing values
print("Missing values:\n", df.isnull().sum())

# Remove duplicates
df = df.drop_duplicates()

# Fill missing values
df = df.fillna(method='ffill')

# Save cleaned data
df.to_csv('data/cleaned_data.csv', index=False)

print("Data cleaning completed.")

